Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.86,0:00:05.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪(葉山)少し いいかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.69,0:00:06.19,Default,Hayama,0,0,0,,Got a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.86,0:00:07.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(比企谷)何だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.19,0:00:06.90,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.59,0:00:10.89,Default,Hayama,0,0,0,,I wanted to talk to you about what to do on Saturday.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.91,0:00:09.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(葉山)土曜日の時間について
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.86,0:00:12.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ちょっと相談したいんだけど\Nはッ？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.89,0:00:11.65,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.87,0:00:15.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もしかして聞いてないか？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.13,0:00:15.26,Default,Hayama,0,0,0,,Wait, didn't you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.26,0:00:17.21,Default,Hayama,0,0,0,,I was talking to Orimoto-san via e-mail,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.52,0:00:19.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,折本さんとメールしてたら\N土曜日 遊びに行こうって
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.21,0:00:19.06,Default,Hayama,0,0,0,,and we decided to hang out on Saturday.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.06,0:00:20.91,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,No, I didn't hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.54,0:00:22.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや 聞いてねえけど
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.64,0:00:25.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃ 一緒に行かないか？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.95,0:00:24.91,Default,Hayama,0,0,0,,Then, want to come along?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.91,0:00:26.55,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.35,0:00:27.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,行くわけねえだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.83,0:00:31.17,Default,Hayama,0,0,0,,Will you think of it as a favor to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.87,0:00:31.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,助けると思って\N来てくれないか
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.54,0:00:34.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺じゃ助けにならないし
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.66,0:00:34.70,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,I can't be of any help to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.54,0:00:38.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前は そもそも\N助けがいるようなヤツじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.70,0:00:37.43,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,You're not the type who'd need help with that, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.94,0:00:40.68,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,Besides, I don't want to go out on a day off.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.54,0:00:41.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それに\N休みの日まで外出たくねえよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.05,0:00:45.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうか
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.14,0:00:44.44,Default,Hayama,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.05,0:00:47.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(結衣)あッ\N(海老名)うんうん…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.19,0:00:53.94,Default,Komachi,0,0,0,,Hey. Phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.52,0:00:54.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(小町)ねえ 電話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.94,0:00:55.59,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,Huh? Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.53,0:00:56.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はッ？ おッ と
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.20,0:00:57.72,Default,Komachi,0,0,0,,I'm going to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.53,0:00:59.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,小町 もう寝るから\N終わったら そこに置いといて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.72,0:00:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it there when you're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.77,0:01:00.68,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.86,0:01:01.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.01,0:01:05.97,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.52,0:01:08.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もしもし？\N☎(陽乃)ひゃっはろー！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.97,0:01:07.52,Default - Italic,Haruno,0,0,0,,Yahello!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.21,0:01:10.94,iPhone,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8\c&H8C8884&\fscx53\fscy53\pos(625,209)\frz3.438}{TS 01:07}Yukinoshita Haruno
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.61,0:01:18.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.88,0:01:14.23,Default - Italic,Haruno,0,0,0,,Are you fighting with your sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.72,0:01:14.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,☎(陽乃)妹ちゃんとケンカ？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.23,0:01:16.97,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,Not much of one, compared to you and yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.81,0:01:17.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そちらに比べたらｹﾝｶでもない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.17,0:01:19.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,☎アッハハ なるほど～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.03,0:01:19.37,Default - Italic,Haruno,0,0,0,,I hear ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.18,0:01:23.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,☎それより聞いたぞ デートに\N誘われたのに行かなくていいの？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.37,0:01:20.89,Default - Italic,Haruno,0,0,0,,Anyway, I heard the news.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.89,0:01:23.31,Default - Italic,Haruno,0,0,0,,You were invited on a date, and you don't want to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.70,0:01:25.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誘われてないんですけど
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.26,0:01:26.04,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,I wasn't invited.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.77,0:01:29.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,☎隼人には誘われてるんだし\N行ったらいいのに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.04,0:01:29.31,Default - Italic,Haruno,0,0,0,,Hayato invited you. You should go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.31,0:01:30.72,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,Um, I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.42,0:01:31.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや 行かないでしょ\N☎え～ッ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.72,0:01:35.08,Default - Italic,Haruno,0,0,0,,Aww... Hayato never bows his head to ask favors, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.84,0:01:35.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,☎隼人が人に頭下げて\N頼み事しないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.08,0:01:37.51,Default - Italic,Haruno,0,0,0,,He's got more pride than you'd think.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.23,0:01:38.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,☎あれで結構 プライド高いから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.03,0:01:40.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,☎そうまでして比企谷君を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.32,0:01:43.33,iPhone,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\c&H979291&\fax0.5\fs16\pos(816.793,81.207)\frz310.8}{TS 01:07}Yukinoshita Haruno
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.76,0:01:43.33,Default - Italic,Haruno,0,0,0,,I can't help wondering why he went that far to try to bring you along.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.03,0:01:42.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,☎連れていきたがる理由も
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.03,0:01:44.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,☎気になるのよね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.35,0:01:47.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,☎いいじゃない 昔好きだった子と
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.54,0:01:46.21,Default - Italic,Haruno,0,0,0,,Just go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.21,0:01:49.08,Default - Italic,Haruno,0,0,0,,It'll be romantic to go on a date with your old love!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.19,0:01:50.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,☎デートなんて ロマンチックで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.79,0:01:53.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あれを好きだったとは\N言わないですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.40,0:01:53.59,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,I wouldn't call that "love."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.59,0:01:56.13,Default - Italic,Haruno,0,0,0,,What wouldn't you call "love"?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.71,0:01:56.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,☎どれを好きだったとは\N言わないのかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.63,0:02:00.19,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,I was just pushing my own desires onto her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.70,0:02:00.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただ一方的に\N願望を押しつけてたというか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.19,0:02:03.64,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,It was a mistake. I couldn't call it the real deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.37,0:02:05.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勘違いしてただけで\Nそれを本物とは呼ばない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.02,0:02:09.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,☎アハッ\N君は まるで理性の化け物だね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.77,0:02:09.48,Default - Italic,Haruno,0,0,0,,You're like some kind of logic monster, you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.06,0:02:12.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何すか それ\Nそんなんじゃないですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.48,0:02:12.33,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,What's that supposed to mean? It's nothing like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.33,0:02:15.65,Default - Italic,Haruno,0,0,0,,Okay... Then you're a self-consciousness monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.35,0:02:15.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,☎そっか じゃ 自意識の化け物だ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.02,0:02:21.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,☎とにかく！\Nデートには ちゃんと行くこと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.40,0:02:18.45,iPhone,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\c&H979291&\fax0.5\fs16\pos(816.793,81.207)\frz310.8}{TS 01:07}Yukinoshita Haruno
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.40,0:02:21.52,Default - Italic,Haruno,0,0,0,,Anyway! You're going on the date!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.35,0:02:25.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,☎じゃないと\N家まで迎えに行っちゃうからね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.52,0:02:24.27,Default - Italic,Haruno,0,0,0,,If you don't, I'll come to your house and drag you out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.04,0:02:27.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ため息)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.03,0:02:33.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(葉山)悪い 付き合ってもらって
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.29,0:02:32.92,Default,Hayama,0,0,0,,Sorry to have you come along.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.92,0:02:35.71,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,I only came because Yukinoshita's sister scares me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.10,0:02:35.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,雪ノ下姉が怖いから来ただけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.71,0:02:37.59,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,Thank her, not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.72,0:02:37.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,礼なら そっちに言っとけよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.59,0:02:40.34,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,And why'd you move this to a weekday just to get me to...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.80,0:02:40.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つ～か 平日にしてまで俺を…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.34,0:02:42.51,Default,Hayama,0,0,0,,Oh, isn't that them?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.41,0:02:42.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あッ あれじゃないか？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.36,0:02:44.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(折本)お待たせ～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.51,0:02:44.26,Default,Kaori,0,0,0,,Sorry we're late!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.36,0:02:47.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃあ 行こうか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.06,0:02:47.27,Default,Hayama,0,0,0,,Ready to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.03,0:02:53.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まずは映画からだっけ？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.44,0:02:53.01,Default,Hayama,0,0,0,,Were we going to a movie first?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.01,0:02:55.48,Default,Kaori,0,0,0,,Yeah! I want to see a movie!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.04,0:02:55.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うん 映画見たいよね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.04,0:02:57.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(仲町)見に行こう 見に行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.48,0:02:56.69,Default,Chika,0,0,0,,Let's go see one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.69,0:02:58.28,Default,Kaori,0,0,0,,What genre should we go for?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.11,0:02:59.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何のｼﾞｬﾝﾙがいいかな\Nう～ん➡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.28,0:03:00.12,Default,Chika,0,0,0,,Hmm... Romance?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.04,0:03:01.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,恋愛？\Nだよね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.12,0:03:00.95,Default,Kaori,0,0,0,,Yeah, totally!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.35,0:03:12.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(折本)比企谷と映画とか
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.60,0:03:12.21,Default,Kaori,0,0,0,,I can't believe I'm seeing a movie with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.36,0:03:16.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,マジ 中学の友達 聞いたら\N絶対 ビビるよね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.67,0:03:16.35,Default,Kaori,0,0,0,,If I told the girls from middle school about this, they'd freak!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.35,0:03:17.25,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.36,0:03:18.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だろうな\Nだよね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.25,0:03:18.54,Default,Kaori,0,0,0,,Totally!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.35,0:03:27.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,<思い返してみれば>
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.68,0:03:29.68,Default - Italic,Hachi,0,0,0,,Looking back, I feel like this is how it was in middle school, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.35,0:03:30.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,<中学の頃も こうだった気がする>
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.36,0:03:35.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,<一度たりとて 俺達の距離が\N縮まったことなどなかったのだ>
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.42,0:03:34.81,Default - Italic,Hachi,0,0,0,,We never once got any closer to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.32,0:03:40.74,Default - Italic,Hachi,0,0,0,,Orimoto Kaori just acts this way toward people she has no interest in, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.35,0:03:39.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,<ただ 折本かおりは\N興味のない人間に対しても>
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.03,0:03:41.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,<こういう接し方をするのだと>
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.45,0:03:43.41,Default - Italic,Hachi,0,0,0,,That's all it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.69,0:03:44.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,<ただ それだけのこと>
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.04,0:03:47.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,<始まってもいなかったものを\N今になって>
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.30,0:03:50.40,Default - Italic,Hachi,0,0,0,,Now, I finally feel like I managed to end something that never started.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.64,0:03:52.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,<ちゃんと終わらせることが\Nできた気がした>
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.00,0:03:55.41,Default,Kaori,0,0,0,,Anyway, that explosion was really huge, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.03,0:03:55.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(折本)ていうか あの爆発\N派手じゃなかった？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.41,0:03:57.61,Default,Kaori,0,0,0,,Hikigaya jumped out of his skin!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.42,0:03:57.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,比企谷とか超キョドってんの
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.52,0:04:00.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,動き キモくて\Nマジ ウケたんだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.61,0:03:59.92,Default,Kaori,0,0,0,,The way he was moving was so creepy, it was hilarious!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.92,0:04:01.88,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,Well, it was louder than I expected...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.09,0:04:02.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや 思ったより音がね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.88,0:04:04.08,Default,Hayama,0,0,0,,Yeah, it startled me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.02,0:04:04.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ ちょっと驚いたな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.02,0:04:07.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも\N葉山君 超落ち着いてなかった？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.08,0:04:06.98,Default,Chika,0,0,0,,But Hayama-kun, you were totally calm, weren't you?
