Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.23,0:06:23.30,Default,Tobe,0,0,0,,All right! Irohas, let's go to Riding Sport!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.36,0:06:23.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よし いろはす\Nライスポ 行くべ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.03,0:06:26.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もういいです\Nﾗｲｽﾎﾟ 野球ﾒｲﾝですし
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.30,0:06:25.93,Default,Iroha,0,0,0,,I'll pass. They have mostly baseball stuff, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.93,0:06:28.97,Default,Hayama,0,0,0,,I guess even Iroha lets you see her that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.08,0:06:29.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いろはも 君には\Nああいう姿を見せるんだな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.97,0:06:29.88,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.04,0:06:31.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はッ？\Nいろはは色んな人に
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.88,0:06:33.19,Default,Hayama,0,0,0,,Iroha wants to look cute to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.04,0:06:33.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,かわいい自分を見せたがる
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.02,0:06:35.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,きっと愛されたいんだろうな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.19,0:06:35.12,Default,Hayama,0,0,0,,I think she wants to be liked.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.36,0:06:38.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから 素を見せるのは珍しいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.50,0:06:37.87,Default,Hayama,0,0,0,,So it's unusual for her to be her real self.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.22,0:06:40.37,Default - Italic,Hachi,0,0,0,,That would mean she can be herself
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.36,0:06:40.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,<それ 俺には愛されたくないから>
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.37,0:06:43.63,Default - Italic,,0,0,0,,around me because she doesn't want me to like her...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.68,0:06:44.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,<素を見せるってことに\Nなっちゃうんだけど>
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.05,0:06:47.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(葉山)中学の時 好きだったって？\Nはッ？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.80,0:06:46.88,Default,Hayama,0,0,0,,So you liked her in middle school, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.88,0:06:49.63,Default,Kaori,0,0,0,,{\a6}Hey, don't you think this one's better?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.21,0:06:47.96,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.69,0:06:51.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああいうのが\Nタイプだったのか？ 意外だな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.96,0:06:49.63,Default,Hayama,0,0,0,,Was that the type you liked?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.63,0:06:50.84,Default,Chika,0,0,0,,{\a6}I'm not sure... I like this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.63,0:06:50.84,Default,Hayama,0,0,0,,Didn't expect that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.84,0:06:51.94,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.84,0:06:52.68,Default,Kaori,0,0,0,,{\a6}This one? Okay, I'll get this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.01,0:06:53.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うるせえよ 別に折本だけじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.94,0:06:53.94,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,It wasn't just Orimoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.54,0:06:57.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,全然違う おとなしい子や\Nもっと騒がしい人が好…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.94,0:06:57.78,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,There were much quieter girls and noisier girls that I l—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.18,0:06:59.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,タイプだったこともある
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.78,0:06:59.39,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,That were my type, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.18,0:07:02.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そういうの\N好きなタイプとは言わないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.64,0:07:02.27,Default,Hayama,0,0,0,,That's not what you'd call a "type."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.20,0:07:06.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大体 昔 そうだったから\N今もそうだとは限らないだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.27,0:07:06.24,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,Just because it was true then doesn't make it true now, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.04,0:07:08.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪(葉山)そうだな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.24,0:07:07.62,Default,Hayama,0,0,0,,True.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.02,0:07:10.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,結局 本当に
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.90,0:07:13.91,Default,Hayama,0,0,0,,We've probably never really, truly liked anyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.69,0:07:14.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人を好きになったことが\Nないんだろうな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.35,0:07:17.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,君も 俺も
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.73,0:07:17.66,Default,Hayama,0,0,0,,You and me both.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.66,0:07:21.46,Default - Italic,Tobe,0,0,0,,I actually think Ebina-san's pretty cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.68,0:07:21.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,《俺 実はさ 海老名さん\Nちょっといいなって思ってんだ》
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.35,0:07:24.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,《隼人君はどうなんよ ねえ》\N《俺は…》
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.46,0:07:24.00,Default - Italic,Tobe,0,0,0,,What about you, Hayato-kun? Huh? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.00,0:07:24.68,Default - Italic,Hayama,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.68,0:07:25.62,Default - Italic,Tobe,0,0,0,,C'mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.74,0:07:26.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,《ちょっと》\N《やめておこう》
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.62,0:07:26.85,Default - Italic,Hayama,0,0,0,,Nah, I'm saying nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.84,0:07:31.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,《ちょっ 隼人君 それないって\Nイニシャルでいいから》
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.85,0:07:29.51,Default - Italic,Tobe,0,0,0,,C'mon! That's no fair, Hayato-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.51,0:07:30.84,Default - Italic,Tobe,0,0,0,,Just give me an initial!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.36,0:07:33.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,《(ため息)》
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.35,0:07:36.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,《≪(葉山)Ｙ…》
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.61,0:07:35.83,Default - Italic,Hayama,0,0,0,,Y.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.37,0:07:39.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから 勘違いしていたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.97,0:07:39.33,Default,Hayama,0,0,0,,I guess that's why I had the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.37,0:07:44.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪(葉山)ちょっと\Nおなか減らない？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.97,0:07:44.35,Default,Hayama,0,0,0,,Are you hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.34,0:07:46.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(折本)減った！\N(葉山)何食べる？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.35,0:07:45.54,Default,Kaori,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.54,0:07:46.73,Default,Hayama,0,0,0,,What do you want to eat, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.73,0:07:48.01,Default,Chika,0,0,0,,Anything's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.78,0:07:49.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何でもいいよ\N何食べよっか？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.01,0:07:49.86,Default,Kaori,0,0,0,,What should we eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.43,0:07:54.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,サイゼ とかな\Nえ～ッ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.66,0:07:53.49,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,Maybe... Saize?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.49,0:07:54.52,Default,Chika,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.52,0:07:56.49,Default - Italic,Hachi,0,0,0,,You said anything was good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.55,0:07:56.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,<何でもいいって言ったろ>
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.51,0:08:00.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,<何 サイゼ嫌なの？\Nそれとも 俺のことが嫌なの？>
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.97,0:08:00.83,Default - Italic,Hachi,0,0,0,,What? You don't like Saize? Or you don't like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.40,0:08:00.83,Default,Kaori,0,0,0,,{\a6}Saize? Saize?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.53,0:08:03.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まあ あんまり重いのも何だし➡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.83,0:08:03.33,Default,Hayama,0,0,0,,Well, we probably don't want anything that heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.33,0:08:05.32,Default,Hayama,0,0,0,,How about that café?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.56,0:08:05.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そこのカフェでいいかな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.68,0:08:07.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪(仲町)メッチャおいしかったね
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.83,0:08:07.59,Default,Chika,0,0,0,,The food here is so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.59,0:08:09.16,Default,Kaori,0,0,0,,I know! It's awesome! And so trendy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.73,0:08:11.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,メッチャおいしい\Nしかもオシャレだしね
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.16,0:08:10.42,Default,Chika,0,0,0,,I'm so full.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.42,0:08:13.22,Default,Chika,0,0,0,,I know, right? Trust Hayama-kun to pick a good one!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.02,0:08:13.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,葉山君のチョイス\Nさすが
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.02,0:08:16.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪(折本)さすがだね\N≪(仲町)それに比べて
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.22,0:08:13.76,Default,Kaori,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.76,0:08:15.09,Default,Chika,0,0,0,,Compared to Saize...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.09,0:08:17.29,Default,Kaori,0,0,0,,Whoa... You're going there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.08,0:08:18.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪(折本)それ言っちゃう？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.29,0:08:18.35,Default,Chika,0,0,0,,I'm... not, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.35,0:08:19.89,Default - Italic,Hachi,0,0,0,,Oh, come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.36,0:08:20.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,<おいおい>
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.89,0:08:23.45,Default,Kaori,0,0,0,,Seriously, though, who suggests Saize?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.35,0:08:24.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかしね サイゼはないわ\Nちょっとね
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.45,0:08:24.85,Default,Chika,0,0,0,,Yeah, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.68,0:08:27.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何言ってんのか\N理解するのに時間が…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.85,0:08:28.59,Default,Kaori,0,0,0,,It took me ages to figure out what he was even talking about at first!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.29,0:08:28.59,Default,Chika,0,0,0,,{\a6}I know what you mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.70,0:08:29.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分かる～\Nやっぱね➡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.59,0:08:29.44,Default,Kaori,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.59,0:08:29.44,Default,Chika,0,0,0,,{\a6}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.44,0:08:31.06,Default,Chika,0,0,0,,I'm so glad we came to this café.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.69,0:08:32.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このカフェで\Nよかったね
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.55,0:08:31.49,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.04,0:08:35.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪(葉山)そういうの\Nあまり好きじゃないな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.18,0:08:35.22,Default,Hayama,0,0,0,,I don't like it when people do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.03,0:08:38.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(二人)えッ？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.37,0:08:43.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ だよね～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.01,0:08:43.79,Default,Chika,0,0,0,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.74,0:08:45.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ そうじゃないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.79,0:08:45.50,Default,Hayama,0,0,0,,No, I don't mean that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.79,0:08:48.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺が言ってるのは君達のことさ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.80,0:08:48.25,Default,Hayama,0,0,0,,I'm talking about you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.36,0:08:50.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(二人)えッ？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.34,0:08:55.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,え えっと… ねえ？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.74,0:08:53.89,Default,Chika,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.89,0:08:55.40,Default,Chika,0,0,0,,R-Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.37,0:08:57.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うん…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.40,0:08:56.51,Default,Kaori,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.38,0:09:00.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(足音)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.27,0:09:02.10,Default,Hayama,0,0,0,,Oh, they're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.47,0:09:02.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あッ 来たか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.69,0:09:07.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うん？\Nお前ら
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.51,0:09:07.73,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,You guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.81,0:09:10.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ヒッキー
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.21,0:09:10.82,Default,Yui,0,0,0,,Hikki...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.37,0:09:15.90,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.80,0:09:17.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何で ここに…\N俺が呼んだんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.90,0:09:17.71,Default,Hayama,0,0,0,,I called them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.44,0:09:25.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,比企谷は君達が\N思っている程度のヤツじゃない➡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.91,0:09:25.46,Default,Hayama,0,0,0,,Hikigaya isn't the loser you two think he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.09,0:09:28.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,君達より ずっと\N素敵な子達と親しくしている
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.94,0:09:29.40,Default,Hayama,0,0,0,,He's friends with girls who are much cooler than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.76,0:09:30.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えッ？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.42,0:09:34.34,Default,Hayama,0,0,0,,Could you stop making selfish comments after making only surface judgments?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.78,0:09:33.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,表面だけ見て 勝手なこと言うのは
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.29,0:09:36.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やめてくれないかな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.49,0:09:42.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ため息)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.56,0:09:45.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(折本)ごめん 帰るね
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.84,0:09:44.60,Default,Kaori,0,0,0,,Sorry. I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.13,0:09:48.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ うん… ごめん 私も
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.21,0:09:46.66,Default,Chika,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.66,0:09:48.98,Default,Chika,0,0,0,,Sorry... I'm going, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.77,0:09:56.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そっか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.20,0:09:56.61,Default,Kaori,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.62,0:10:06.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(雪乃)選挙の打ち合わせ\Nと聞いていたけれど
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.14,0:10:06.62,Default,Yukino,0,0,0,,I was told we were meeting to discuss the election.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.60,0:10:09.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,選挙って 生徒会のか？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.62,0:10:09.00,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,Election? The student council one?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.12,0:10:16.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あのね 隼人君に\N選挙に出てもらえないかって
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.29,0:10:18.84,Default,Yui,0,0,0,,Uh, actually, we thought we'd ask Hayato-kun to run in the election... so we...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.78,0:10:20.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それで 今日…\Nそうか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.84,0:10:19.89,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.20,0:10:22.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,<葉山を候補に立てる>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.29,0:10:22.42,Default - Italic,Hachi,0,0,0,,Putting Hayama in the running...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.42,0:10:24.89,Default - Italic,Hachi,0,0,0,,There's nothing strange about that choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.44,0:10:26.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,<その選択自体に\N不思議はない ただ…>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.89,0:10:26.07,Default - Italic,Hachi,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.07,0:10:29.69,Default,Hayama,0,0,0,,I just wanted to do whatever I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.11,0:10:29.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺はただ できることをやろうと\N思っただけだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.69,0:10:32.81,Default,Haruno,0,0,0,,Hmm... I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.94,0:10:32.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(陽乃)ふ～ん なるほどね
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.45,0:10:34.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,姉さん！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.18,0:10:34.36,Default,Yukino,0,0,0,,Nee-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.36,0:10:37.49,Default,Haruno,0,0,0,,So you're not going to be student council president, Yukino-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.45,0:10:38.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(陽乃)雪乃ちゃんが生徒会長\Nやるんじゃないんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.55,0:10:41.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,てっきり そうすると思ったのに
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.57,0:10:40.66,Default,Haruno,0,0,0,,And I was sure that's what you'd do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.21,0:10:47.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうやって\N誰かにやらせたり 押しつけるの
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.41,0:10:49.28,Default,Haruno,0,0,0,,The way you push things like that onto others is just like Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.11,0:10:50.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お母さん そっくり➡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.11,0:10:53.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まあ\N雪乃ちゃんは それでいいかもね
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.17,0:10:53.46,Default,Haruno,0,0,0,,But maybe that's fine for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.78,0:10:57.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あなたは\N何もやらなくていいんだもの➡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.17,0:10:57.17,Default,Haruno,0,0,0,,You don't need to do anything, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.44,0:11:01.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いつも誰かが やってくれるもんね
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.78,0:11:00.18,Default,Haruno,0,0,0,,Someone else will always do it for you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.11,0:11:03.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(手を払う音)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.16,0:11:10.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そう そういうこと
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.30,0:11:09.98,Default,Yukino,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.45,0:11:17.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,他に話がないなら 私は帰るわ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.48,0:11:16.91,Default,Yukino,0,0,0,,If there's nothing else to discuss, I'm leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.12,0:11:21.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,待って ゆきのん！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.19,0:11:19.74,Default,Yui,0,0,0,,W-Wait, Yukinon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.11,0:11:27.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何で わざわざ\N雪ノ下に あんなことを
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.98,0:11:27.63,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,Why did you do that to Yukinoshita?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.50,0:11:30.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,聞くまでもないんじゃない？\Nいつものことよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.63,0:11:30.58,Default,Haruno,0,0,0,,You even have to ask? It's just the usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.79,0:11:32.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,単なる ちょっかいにしちゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.01,0:11:33.89,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,That was too elaborate to say you were just messing with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.79,0:11:35.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,手間かけすぎでしょ\Nそう？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.89,0:11:34.96,Default,Haruno,0,0,0,,Was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.11,0:11:41.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まあ 俺も妹いるんで そういうの\N分からんでもないんですけど
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.80,0:11:40.99,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,Well, I have a little sister myself, so it's not like I don't understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.77,0:11:46.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,比企谷君は\N何でも分かっちゃうんだね
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.97,0:11:45.97,Default,Haruno,0,0,0,,You understand everything, don't you, Hikigaya-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.45,0:11:51.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな怖い顔しないでよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.00,0:11:51.68,Default,Haruno,0,0,0,,Don't make that scary face.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.49,0:11:53.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本当に感心してるんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.68,0:11:53.69,Default,Haruno,0,0,0,,I'm honestly impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.69,0:11:55.40,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,Well, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.78,0:11:55.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それは どうも
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.40,0:11:57.29,Default,Haruno,0,0,0,,You're so interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.78,0:12:01.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,君は面白いね いつも そうやって\N言葉や行動の裏を読もうとする
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.29,0:12:01.08,Default,Haruno,0,0,0,,You always try to read what's behind every word and action.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.08,0:12:03.99,Default,Haruno,0,0,0,,I kind of like that, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.38,0:12:04.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そういうの私 結構 好きだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.12,0:12:09.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悪意に おびえてるみたいで\Nかわいいもの
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.25,0:12:09.66,Default,Haruno,0,0,0,,It's so cute, like you're afraid everyone has evil intentions.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.66,0:12:12.19,Default,Haruno,0,0,0,,There's nothing interesting about someone who can handle
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.71,0:12:15.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何でも そつなくこなす人間なんて\N面白みがないじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.19,0:12:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,everything flawlessly, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.45,0:12:21.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さ～て 気になってたことも\N分かったし 私も帰ろうかな
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.92,0:12:19.17,Default,Haruno,0,0,0,,Well, I found out what I wanted to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.17,0:12:20.92,Default,Haruno,0,0,0,,I guess I'll get going, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.92,0:12:23.41,Default,Haruno,0,0,0,,This is boring now, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.19,0:12:24.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,な～んか しらけちゃったし
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.11,0:12:30.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,余計な気 回してんじゃねえよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.70,0:12:30.77,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,Don't get weird ideas like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.45,0:12:33.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなつもりはないんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.77,0:12:32.93,Default,Hayama,0,0,0,,That wasn't my intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.93,0:12:36.03,Default,Hayama,0,0,0,,I only did what I wanted to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.12,0:12:36.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただ俺が\Nやりたいことをしただけなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.69,0:12:39.86,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,Including what you said to Orimoto and her friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.79,0:12:39.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さっきの\N折本達に言ったのもか？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.44,0:12:43.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいのか あんなことして
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.69,0:12:43.80,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,You sure that was a good idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.80,0:12:47.12,Default,Hayama,0,0,0,,I'm in a crappy mood now. I never want to do it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.94,0:12:47.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最低の気分だよ 二度としたくない
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.95,0:12:51.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だったら やんなきゃいいだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.18,0:12:49.79,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,Then you shouldn't have done it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.10,0:12:54.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,座らないか
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.60,0:12:54.16,Default,Hayama,0,0,0,,Gonna sit down?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.78,0:13:03.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ずっと考えていたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.40,0:13:03.30,Default,Hayama,0,0,0,,I've been thinking all this time
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.43,0:13:05.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺が壊してしまったものを
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.71,0:13:06.84,Default,Hayama,0,0,0,,of how I can get back what I destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.43,0:13:08.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,取り返す方法を\Nはッ？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.84,0:13:08.30,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.30,0:13:11.48,Default,Hayama,0,0,0,,I put my hopes in you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.43,0:13:11.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は君に 期待していて
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.48,0:13:14.73,Default,Hayama,0,0,0,,That's why I relied on you, even though I knew how you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.50,0:13:15.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから 分かっていたのに\N頼ってしまった➡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.44,0:13:18.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのせいで 君は…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.60,0:13:18.13,Default,Hayama,0,0,0,,And because of that, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.09,0:13:20.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おい
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.93,0:13:19.93,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.93,0:13:22.77,Default,Hayama,0,0,0,,You need to realize how much you're worth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.11,0:13:23.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,君は\N自分の価値を正しく知るべきだ➡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.77,0:13:25.11,Default,Hayama,0,0,0,,And so do the people around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.12,0:13:25.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,君だけじゃない 周りも
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.70,0:13:28.37,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,What are you... Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.78,0:13:28.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前 何言って… はッ？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.37,0:13:31.12,Default,Hayama,0,0,0,,But that's hard to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.44,0:13:30.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただ それは難しいことで
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.77,0:13:34.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もっと うまくやれれば\Nよかったんだけどな➡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.12,0:13:34.12,Default,Hayama,0,0,0,,I wish I'd done it better.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.29,0:13:37.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺が できるのは\Nこれくらいしかなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.75,0:13:37.42,Default,Hayama,0,0,0,,But this was all I could do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.81,0:13:41.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,君は ずっと\Nこんなふうにしてきたんだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.85,0:13:40.26,Default,Hayama,0,0,0,,This is how you've always lived, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.43,0:13:43.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう やめないか
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.19,0:13:45.42,Default,Hayama,0,0,0,,Why don't you stop making yourself a sacrifice?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.49,0:13:46.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自分を犠牲にするのは
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.42,0:13:48.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一緒にするな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.77,0:13:48.43,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,Don't put me on your level.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.42,0:13:50.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,犠牲？ ふざけんな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.43,0:13:50.60,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,Sacrifice? That's bull.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.60,0:13:54.27,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,This is what's natural for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.84,0:13:54.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当たり前のことなんだよ\N俺にとっては
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.11,0:13:56.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いつも一人だからな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.27,0:13:56.35,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,Because I'm always alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.12,0:13:59.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから\N周囲がどうとか関係ねえんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.35,0:13:59.35,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,So what everyone else thinks doesn't mean a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.45,0:14:04.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺の目の前で起きることは\Nいつだって俺の出来事でしかない
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.72,0:14:03.86,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,Whatever happens in front of me happens to me, and me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.86,0:14:06.11,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,Don't get weird ideas and try to butt in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.11,0:14:07.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勘違いして割り込んでくんな
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.11,0:14:09.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,君が誰かを助けるのは
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.21,0:14:09.11,Default,Hayama,0,0,0,,Isn't the reason you help people
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.45,0:14:14.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誰かに助けられたいと\N願っているからじゃないのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.46,0:14:12.70,Default,Hayama,0,0,0,,because you want someone to help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.49,0:14:20.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,違えよ\N気持ち悪い同情を押しつけて
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.64,0:14:18.00,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.00,0:14:19.96,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,Don't force your disgusting idea of sympathy onto me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.96,0:14:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need your pity.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.14,0:14:23.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝手に哀れんでんじゃねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.34,0:14:31.34,Sharpie,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8\fscx60\fscy60\fax0.7\frz319.6\pos(701.714,453.714)\c&H483C33&}{TS 15:59}H{*\c&H463A31&}i{*\c&H45382E&}k{*\c&H43362C&}i{*\c&H42332A&}g{*\c&H403128&}a{*\c&H3F2F25&}y{\c&H3D2D23&}a
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.78,0:14:32.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふざけんな
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.34,0:14:32.80,Default - Italic,Hachi,0,0,0,,Don't screw with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.77,0:14:35.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,<自己犠牲なんて呼ばせない>
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.84,0:14:36.04,Default - Italic,Hachi,0,0,0,,I won't let you call it self-sacrifice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.79,0:14:38.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,<誰が貴様らのためなんかに>
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.04,0:14:40.37,Default - Italic,Hachi,0,0,0,,Why the hell would I sacrifice myself for any of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.11,0:14:40.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,<犠牲になってやるものか>
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.37,0:14:44.61,Default - Italic,Hachi,0,0,0,,Even if I didn't say it out loud, I had my own solid conviction.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.44,0:14:42.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,<言葉には ならずとも>
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.49,0:14:45.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,<俺には確かな信念があったのだ>
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.45,0:14:48.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,<誰かと たった一つ共有していて>
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.49,0:14:48.36,Default - Italic,Hachi,0,0,0,,The one conviction that I shared with someone else,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.36,0:14:52.47,Default - Italic,Hachi,0,0,0,,and now I've lost it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.45,0:14:52.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,<今はもう\Nなくしてしまった信念が>
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.16,0:15:00.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(平塚)今朝 雪ノ下が話しに来たよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.56,0:15:00.04,Default,Hira,0,0,0,,Yukinoshita came to talk to me this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.04,0:15:03.25,Default,Hira,0,0,0,,She says she's entering the running for student council president.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.11,0:15:03.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,生徒会長選に立候補するそうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.77,0:15:06.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうですか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.93,0:15:06.05,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.20,0:15:11.68,Default,Hira,0,0,0,,Hikigaya, what will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.22,0:15:11.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,比企谷\N君はどうする？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.44,0:15:13.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうもしませんよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.68,0:15:13.27,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.27,0:15:16.96,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,Speaking strictly of credentials, she's fit for the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.44,0:15:17.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,単純な資質だけをいえば\Nあいつが適任でしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.76,0:15:23.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだな 教師達はじめ\N他の連中が知れば大歓迎だろう
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.10,0:15:19.63,Default,Hira,0,0,0,,True.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.63,0:15:23.25,Default,Hira,0,0,0,,When the teachers and everyone else finds out, they should be thrilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.25,0:15:25.61,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,You haven't told anyone yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.45,0:15:25.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まだ誰にも言ってないんですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.61,0:15:27.14,Default,Hira,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.95,0:15:29.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ さて\Nもう一度 聞こう
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.14,0:15:29.36,Default,Hira,0,0,0,,So let me ask you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.29,0:15:32.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,比企谷\N君はどうする？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.36,0:15:32.61,Default,Hira,0,0,0,,Hikigaya, what will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.12,0:15:38.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,雪ノ下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.62,0:15:38.12,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,Yukinoshita.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.12,0:15:43.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前\N自分が立候補するつもりなのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.70,0:15:42.83,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,You plan to announce your candidacy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.11,0:15:45.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えッ？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.17,0:15:48.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,聞いてなかったのか\Nうん…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.59,0:15:47.71,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,You didn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.71,0:15:48.61,Default,Yui,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.11,0:15:51.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これから\N相談するつもりだったのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.61,0:15:50.80,Default,Yukino,0,0,0,,I was just about to discuss it with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.80,0:15:52.84,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,I wouldn't call that a discussion.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.10,0:15:53.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それは相談とは言わねえよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.84,0:15:55.30,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,Is it because of what your sister said?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.12,0:15:55.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前 姉が ああ言ったからか？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.30,0:15:58.36,Default,Yukino,0,0,0,,That has nothing to do with it. This is my decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.45,0:15:58.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,関係ないわ これは私の意思よ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.36,0:15:59.89,Default,Yui,0,0,0,,Yukinon, will the club...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.45,0:16:01.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ゆきのん 部活は？\N大丈夫よ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.89,0:16:01.43,Default,Yukino,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.11,0:16:04.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この部活は\Nそれほど大変ではないし
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.43,0:16:04.72,Default,Yukino,0,0,0,,This club isn't that demanding,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.44,0:16:08.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,生徒会活動についても\N理解はしているから
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.72,0:16:08.01,Default,Yukino,0,0,0,,and I understand the work that comes with being on the student council.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.01,0:16:10.07,Default,Yukino,0,0,0,,It won't place much strain on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.11,0:16:10.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなに負担にならないわ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.07,0:16:12.25,Default,Yukino,0,0,0,,Objectively speaking,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.12,0:16:12.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,客観的に考えて
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.10,0:16:14.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私がやるのが最善だと思う
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.25,0:16:14.61,Default,Yukino,0,0,0,,my doing this was the best choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.61,0:16:18.52,Default,Yukino,0,0,0,,Even against Isshiki-san, I can win easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.79,0:16:18.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一色さん相手でも\N問題なく勝てるわ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.46,0:16:20.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それに
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.52,0:16:19.53,Default,Yukino,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.12,0:16:23.54,Default,Yukino,0,0,0,,And I don't mind doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.43,0:16:23.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それに\N私は やっても構わないもの
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.48,0:16:28.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それは そうかもしれねえけど\Nそもそも勝負しないって手もある
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.54,0:16:27.95,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,That may be, but not trying at all is also an option.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.95,0:16:31.15,Default,Yukino,0,0,0,,Are you talking about your own suggestion?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.17,0:16:31.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それは あなたの案のことを\N言っているの？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.12,0:16:33.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.15,0:16:32.30,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.05,0:16:35.91,Default,Yukino,0,0,0,,Thinking that anything you say or do
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.12,0:16:35.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あなた一人の言葉や態度だけで
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.61,0:16:38.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,全校生徒が動くなんて\N思い上がりよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.91,0:16:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,will move the entire student body is arrogant.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.23,0:16:44.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だったら\Nその上で やり方を考えるだけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.24,0:16:43.67,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,Then I just have to think of how to do it with that in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.10,0:16:49.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,全ての人が あなたを気にかけて
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.27,0:16:49.43,Default,Yukino,0,0,0,,Thinking that everyone concerns themselves with you
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.43,0:16:51.94,Default,Yukino,0,0,0,,enough to hate you is overly self-conscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.54,0:16:52.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,嫌っているなんて 自意識過剰だわ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.09,0:16:58.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あなたと私のやり方は違う
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.68,0:16:58.16,Default,Yukino,0,0,0,,You and I don't go about things the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.11,0:17:01.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.41,0:17:00.72,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,True.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.45,0:17:06.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そっか\Nゆきのんは そうするんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.85,0:17:06.71,Default,Yui,0,0,0,,I see... So that's what you're going to do, Yukinon...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.78,0:17:16.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ちょっ ちょっと待って！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.79,0:17:15.93,Default,Yui,0,0,0,,W-Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.77,0:17:22.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一緒に帰ろう
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.95,0:17:21.71,Default,Yui,0,0,0,,Let's walk home together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.22,0:17:28.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ゆきのんさ 出るんだね 選挙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.30,0:17:25.69,Default,Yui,0,0,0,,So Yukinon's
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.69,0:17:28.30,Default,Yui,0,0,0,,gonna run in the election, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.13,0:17:31.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.37,0:17:30.35,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.11,0:17:36.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私も\N私も やってみようと思うの
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.25,0:17:33.99,Default,Yui,0,0,0,,I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.99,0:17:36.49,Default,Yui,0,0,0,,I think I'll try it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.20,0:17:38.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はッ？ やるって
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.49,0:17:37.45,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.45,0:17:40.90,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,Try... You mean you'll run, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.44,0:17:41.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前も選挙に出るってことか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.11,0:17:43.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.11,0:17:45.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前 何で？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.25,0:17:45.30,Default,HAchi,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.30,0:17:47.87,Default,Yui,0,0,0,,Because I don't have anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.49,0:17:48.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私さ 何もないから
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.18,0:17:54.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,できることも やれることも\N何もないんだなって
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.38,0:17:54.66,Default,Yui,0,0,0,,There's nothing that I can do at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.45,0:17:59.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから 逆に\Nそういうのもありかな～ とか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.66,0:17:59.22,Default,Yui,0,0,0,,So I thought, on the other hand, that might be a good thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.11,0:18:02.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,逆にって 勝手にそんなこと
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.22,0:18:00.81,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,"On the other hand"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.81,0:18:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't make a selfish decision like—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.16,0:18:04.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝手じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.22,0:18:03.48,Default,Yui,0,0,0,,It's not selfish!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.10,0:18:08.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝手なのは みんなだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.48,0:18:07.60,Default,Yui,0,0,0,,It's everyone else who's selfish!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.10,0:18:11.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前 よく考えたのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.31,0:18:11.15,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,Have you thought this out?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.10,0:18:16.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,考えたよ ちゃんと考えて\Nこれしかないって思って
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.15,0:18:12.69,Default,Yui,0,0,0,,I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.69,0:18:16.11,Default,Yui,0,0,0,,I thought about it and realized it's my only choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.11,0:18:22.24,Default,Yui,0,0,0,,This time, I'm going to work hard myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.11,0:18:23.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今度はね\N私が頑張るの
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.10,0:18:29.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今まで ずっとヒッキーに\N頼ってたんだって 気づいたから
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.12,0:18:28.38,Default,Yui,0,0,0,,I realized that I've always just relied on you before.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.44,0:18:32.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は何もしてねえよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.98,0:18:31.88,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,I didn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.88,0:18:33.42,Default,Yui,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.12,0:18:34.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.09,0:18:37.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだ だから頑張る必要もない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.13,0:18:35.27,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.27,0:18:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So you don't have to work that hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.22,0:18:39.00,Default,Yui,0,0,0,,That's not the only reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.43,0:18:40.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それだけじゃないよ\Nえッ？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.43,0:18:43.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ゆきのんが生徒会長になったらさ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.68,0:18:43.39,Default,Yui,0,0,0,,If Yukinon becomes student council president,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.44,0:18:47.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今までの誰よりも\Nすごい生徒会長になって
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.69,0:18:47.05,Default,Yui,0,0,0,,she'll be the best student council president the school's ever had.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.05,0:18:49.39,Default,Yui,0,0,0,,It'll be good for the school, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.11,0:18:49.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,学校のためにもなって
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.44,0:18:53.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも たぶん\Nこの部活は なくなっちゃうよね
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.66,0:18:54.15,Default,Yui,0,0,0,,But it would probably be the end of our club.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.88,0:18:56.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,別に なくなったりはしないだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.15,0:18:56.26,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,The club won't go anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.26,0:18:57.97,Default,Yui,0,0,0,,It will.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.48,0:18:58.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なくなっちゃうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.43,0:19:03.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,文化祭の時だって ゆきのん\N一つのことに集中するの
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.65,0:19:00.56,Default,Yui,0,0,0,,Just like with the cultural festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.56,0:19:05.91,Default,Yui,0,0,0,,You know Yukinon only focuses on one thing at a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.44,0:19:06.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ヒッキーだって知ってるじゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.09,0:19:10.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私ね
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.20,0:19:09.41,Default,Yui,0,0,0,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.16,0:19:14.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私 この部活 好きなの
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.42,0:19:14.38,Default,Yui,0,0,0,,I like this club.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.77,0:19:19.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,好き なの
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.86,0:19:19.76,Default,Yui,0,0,0,,I... like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.13,0:19:26.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや～ その
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.28,0:19:28.37,Default,Yui,0,0,0,,W-Well, you know... Even if I end up as president,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.09,0:19:29.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私が生徒会長になっても\N結構 適当にやれば
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.37,0:19:29.97,Default,Yui,0,0,0,,I could just do whatever to get by,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.61,0:19:33.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,部活も このまま\Nできるんじゃないかなって
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.97,0:19:32.74,Default,Yui,0,0,0,,and then I'd be able to stay in the club.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.74,0:19:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, it's me we're talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.12,0:19:37.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほら 私だし 周りも\Nそんな期待しないっていうか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.50,0:19:37.39,Default,Yui,0,0,0,,People don't expect much of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.62,0:19:42.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから ゆきのんに勝つよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.86,0:19:40.03,Default,Yui,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.86,0:19:42.78,Default,Yui,0,0,0,,I'll beat Yukinon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.78,0:19:46.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,由比ヶ…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.17,0:19:46.78,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,Yuiga—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.78,0:19:49.35,Default,Yui,0,0,0,,Oh, I'll be fine from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.83,0:19:50.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あッ 私 ここでいいや\Nじゃあね
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.35,0:19:50.72,Default,Yui,0,0,0,,S-See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.72,0:19:51.91,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.77,0:19:52.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ ああ…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.79,0:19:57.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バイバイ ヒッキー
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.93,0:19:57.38,Default,Yui,0,0,0,,Bye-bye, Hikki.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.12,0:20:07.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,<雪ノ下も由比ヶ浜も\N納得した上での選択なら>
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.24,0:20:07.62,Default - Italic,Hachi,0,0,0,,If it's a choice both Yukinoshita and Yuigahama can live with,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.62,0:20:09.56,Default - Italic,Hachi,0,0,0,,I'm fine with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.79,0:20:11.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,<それで構わない ただ…>
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.12,0:20:11.22,Default - Italic,Hachi,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.13,0:20:15.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ため息)
